languages.text: "Когда ты в последний раз покидала поместье, Вистенца? Одного взгляда на джунгли Януса хватит, чтобы понять — что бы ты ни творила якобы на благо планете, ты лишь губишь ее!"

languages.text: "When was the last time you left the estate, Vistenza? Take one look at the jungles of Janus and you'll see that whatever you may have thought you were doing for the good of the planet, you are actually killing it!"

languages.text: “你最后一次离开庄园，已经是什么时候了，维丝坦萨？只要你亲眼看看加努斯的丛林，你就会意识到，无论你怎么认为自己是在为这颗行星的利益服务，你实际上都是在扼杀它！”

languages.text: «¿Cuándo fue la última vez que dejó esta finca, Vistenza? Eche un vistazo a las selvas de Janus y verá que, por mucho que piense que está actuando para bien del planeta, ¡el resultado de sus acciones lo está matando!».
languages.original_text: "When was the last time you left the estate, Vistenza? Take one look at the jungles of Janus and you'll see that whatever you may have thought you were doing for the good of the planet, you are actually killing it!"

languages.text: 「最後に屋敷から出たのはいつだ、ヴィステンツァ？ヤヌスのジャングルを一目見るがいい。お前はこの惑星のためにあらゆることをしているつもりかもしれないが、実際には惑星を殺しているだけだと気づけたはずだ！」
languages.original_text: "When was the last time you left the estate, Vistenza? Take one look at the jungles of Janus and you'll see that whatever you may have thought you were doing for the good of the planet, you are actually killing it!"

languages.text: "Wann habt Ihr zum letzten Mal das Anwesen verlassen, Vistenza? Ein Blick auf die Dschungel von Janus, und Ihr wisst, dass Eure Gedanken, was Ihr alles Gutes für den Planeten tut, falsch sind, weil Ihr in Wahrheit umbringt!"
languages.original_text: "When was the last time you left the estate, Vistenza? Take one look at the jungles of Janus and you'll see that whatever you may have thought you were doing for the good of the planet, you are actually killing it!"

languages.text: « Vous ne quittez donc jamais votre domaine ? Allez donc faire un tour dans les jungles de Janus, vous comprendrez au premier coup d'œil qu'au lieu d'œuvrer pour le bien de la planète comme vous le croyez, vous la tuez à petit feu ! »

languages.text: "Konağından en son ne zaman çıktın Vistenza? Janus'un ormanlarına bak bir, gezegenin iyiliği için yaptığını düşündüğün artık her neyse aslında ölümüne sebep olduğunu anlayacaksın!"
